	<string name="about_text">A game made for drinking. To start, gather in a circle.
		This game is best played with at least four people. Progress round the circle clockwise with each player taking a single turn.\n\n
		Predefined modes can be selected from the \'Predefined Modes\' tab. These modes can be quickly used to load different levels of drinking.\n\n
		In the \'Custom Preferences\' tab, descriptions of all options can be viewed and can be toggled on or off.
